metadata.name: Summer Time 【夏】
metadata.description:
Wanna spend your time in Summer season like her (Natsu)?

Summer time in Japan is different form my hometown or others ^^
You can travel, go to Matsuri and take a picture in Yukata with your friends.
I think it the one of interesting things in Japan ><

I will share and show you more interesting things in Japan in my eyesight that someone don't know about it.
